{"tid":2022891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又bin c] 忘恩負義嘅鄭松泰","createTime":"2020-05-18T15:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:30:59.000Z","uid":41846,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e69a594fdd765116f6263afc695ad797ab8e916","tid":2022891,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SR7cj7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSR7cj7x.png&h=40384c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjLQRd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjLQRd6.png&h=52c2f626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//指不應多謝民主派在席並投下反對票，因投票是他們的職責，若感謝他們，會顯得不尊重他們。//<br />\n<br />\n當年自己差啲被人DQ，講到泛民幫佢係應份，<br />\n唔道謝不特止，<br />\n佢哋一眾熱狗派人士不停狙擊泛民，<br />\n佢哋嗰國師成日宣揚華夏文化，<br />\n但係得人恩果千年記，咁嘅道理都唔識！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-3hgzlwmEJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-3hgzlwmEJs&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=31ca1a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-3hgzlwmEJs</a><br />\n<br />\n自稱又話1對69，<br />\n唔係民主派，係城邦派喎，<br />\n轉頭又話自己民主派<br />\n佢嗰黨友話自己係本土自由派喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/18/230238_ba8eba24f493d67dffd352d96a2a743c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F18%2F230238_ba8eba24f493d67dffd352d96a2a743c.png&h=0607201f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢吓熱狗屌人哋泛民整測速器係會人臉識別，<br />\n但佢又爭取整錄像鏡頭咪侵犯咗老鼠嘅私穩。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815